            <summary>What Is HTML?</summary>
            <p>HTML (HyperText Markup Language) is a 
                standard markup language for creating web pages
            </p>
        </details>

        <details>
           <summary> What is Difference between HTML and CSS?</summary>
            <p>
                HTML is used for structure , while css is used
                for styling and layout
            </p>
        </details>

        <details>
            <summary>What is Semantic tags in HTML?</summary>
            <p>Semantic tags provide meaning to content, like
                article tag, section tag, header tag, footer tag etc
            </p>
        </details>

